title: Luo2027 ( Lucky Uwakwe AMBER)~竞选YFII首届管委会成员
body:
Name :

Luo2027 ( Lucky Uwakwe AMBER)

2. Working experience and related skills introduction

: 6 years working experience in blockchain industry, fintech finance and running project advisor to many successful Blockchain project

3. How much time per week can be used for community governance and discussion :

24 hours per week

4. Why do you want to be a member of the Grant management committee:

I have been part of yfii from earliest days and I interact with the community both English speakers on telegram and Chinese speakers on WeChat, so I know there concern and where it matters most, I volunteer in lots of many group so I know what can help yfii grow well

5. Suggestions for future Grant management (optional) :

No information for now, I will observe and make suggestions in future as we progress thanks
